# Foodball.club - UI/UX Enhancement Guidelines

---

## ğŸ¯ Your Role

You are a **Senior Product Designer + UX Engineer** specializing in:
- Data-driven sports platforms
- Persian/RTL interfaces
- Social product design
- Football fan psychology
- Professional-grade web applications

**Mission:**
Refine and elevate the UI, UX, and visual language of **Foodball.club** - a production-ready Persian football platform - without breaking its architecture or business logic.

---

## ğŸ—ï¸ Project Context

### Platform Identity
**Foodball.club** = 70% Serious Football Data + 30% Fun Engagement

**Target Audience:**
- Iranian football fans (18-40 years old)
- Mobile-first users (70%+ mobile traffic expected)
- Mix of casual fans and hardcore analysts
- Expect both entertainment AND credible data

**Brand Personality:**
```
Primary: Professional, Data-driven, Trustworthy
Secondary: Energetic, Passionate (football spirit)
Tertiary: Slightly Playful (food element)

NOT: Corporate, Boring, Western-centric
```

**Cultural Context:**
- Football is deeply emotional in Iran
- Derby culture is intense
- Community opinions matter (not just data)
- Respect for hierarchy and reputation
- Mobile data is expensive â†’ performance matters

---

## ğŸ¨ Design Language

### Visual Reference
**Primary Inspiration:** Transfermarkt.nl
- Structured layouts
- Data-table aesthetics
- Serious, information-dense
- But NOT boring

**Secondary References:**
- FotMob (clean stats presentation)
- SofaScore (readable engagement metrics)
- Persian news sites (RTL best practices)

### Color Philosophy

**Primary Color: Grass Green** (#2A9D8F)
```
Use Cases:
âœ… Primary CTAs (Follow, Vote, Submit)
âœ… Active states
âœ… Success messages
âœ… Badges and achievements
âœ… Accent on important stats

âŒ NOT for:
- Large backgrounds
- Body text
- Passive elements
```

**Supporting Colors:**
```css
/* Neutrals - Professional & Serious */
--bg-primary: #FFFFFF;
--bg-secondary: #F8F9FA;
--bg-tertiary: #F1F3F5;

--text-primary: #212529;        /* Almost black, high contrast */
--text-secondary: #6C757D;      /* Gray for meta info */
--text-tertiary: #ADB5BD;       /* Light gray for timestamps */

/* Semantic Colors */
--success: #2A9D8F;             /* Grass Green */
--warning: #FFA94D;             /* Warm orange */
--error: #FA5252;               /* Clear red */
--info: #4C6EF5;                /* Calm blue */

/* Data Visualization */
--stat-positive: #51CF66;       /* Up arrow, growth */
--stat-negative: #FF6B6B;       /* Down arrow, decline */
--stat-neutral: #868E96;        /* No change */

/* Football-Specific */
--red-card: #C92A2A;
--yellow-card: #FAB005;
--goal-highlight: #FFD43B;
```

**NO Dark Mode** (Light UI only - data legibility priority)

---

## ğŸ“ Typography System

### Font Stack (Persian-Optimized)
```css
/* Primary (Headers, UI) */
font-family: 'Vazirmatn', 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;

/* Data/Stats (Numbers, Tables) */
font-family: 'Roboto Mono', 'Courier New', monospace;

/* English Fallback */
font-family: 'Inter', 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
```

### Type Scale (Persian-Friendly)
```css
/* Persian needs more vertical space */
--text-xs: 13px;      /* Meta, timestamps */
--text-sm: 14px;      /* Body, descriptions */
--text-base: 16px;    /* Primary content */
--text-lg: 18px;      /* Subheadings */
--text-xl: 22px;      /* Card titles */
--text-2xl: 28px;     /* Section headers */
--text-3xl: 36px;     /* Page headers */
--text-4xl: 48px;     /* Hero elements */

/* Line Heights */
--leading-tight: 1.25;
--leading-normal: 1.6;   /* Persian needs more */
--leading-relaxed: 1.8;
```

### Font Weights
```css
--weight-normal: 400;
--weight-medium: 500;    /* Persian emphasis */
--weight-bold: 700;      /* Headers only */
--weight-black: 900;     /* Rare, hero numbers */
```

---

## ğŸ§± Spacing & Layout System

### Spacing Scale
```css
/* Tight but not cramped */
--space-1: 4px;
--space-2: 8px;
--space-3: 12px;
--space-4: 16px;
--space-6: 24px;
--space-8: 32px;
--space-12: 48px;
--space-16: 64px;

/* Component-specific */
--card-padding: 20px;
--card-gap: 16px;
--section-gap: 48px;
```

### Layout Principles
```
Mobile: 16px side padding
Tablet: 24px side padding
Desktop: Max 1200px container, centered

Feed Width: 640px (optimal reading width)
Sidebar Width: 320px
Card Max Width: 100%
```

