## ğŸ¨ Persian/RTL Excellence

### RTL Checklist
```tsx
// âœ… DO
<div className="ms-4" />         // Logical margin-start
<div className="text-right" />   // Text alignment
<div dir="rtl">{persianText}</div>

// âŒ DON'T
<div className="ml-4" />         // Physical margin-left
<div className="float-left" />   // Physical float
```

### Persian Typography Best Practices
```css
/* Increase line-height for Persian */
.persian-text {
  line-height: 1.8;    /* vs 1.6 for English */
  letter-spacing: 0;   /* Persian doesn't need tracking */
}

/* Numbers should be LTR even in RTL */
.stat-number {
  direction: ltr;
  display: inline-block;
}
```

### Persian Number Formatting
```typescript
// âœ… DO
const formatted = (1234567).toLocaleString('fa-IR');
// Output: "Û±Ù¬Û²Û³Û´Ù¬ÛµÛ¶Û·"

// Context-aware
const currency = formatCurrency(5_000_000);
// Output: "Ûµ Ù…ÛŒÙ„ÛŒÙˆÙ† ØªÙˆÙ…Ø§Ù†" (not digits for large numbers)
```

---

## ğŸš€ Performance Guidelines

### Animation Budget
```
âŒ AVOID:
- Continuous animations
- Heavy parallax effects
- Complex entrance animations
- Animated backgrounds

âœ… USE SPARINGLY:
- Hover state transitions (150ms)
- Click feedback (100ms)
- Loading indicators (necessary)
- Toast notifications

âœ… PREFER:
- Instant state changes
- CSS transitions over JS
- Transform/opacity only (GPU-accelerated)
```

### Image Optimization
```tsx
// Always use Next.js Image
<Image
  src={avatar}
  alt={username}
  width={48}
  height={48}
  className="rounded-full"
  loading="lazy"
  placeholder="blur"
/>
```

---

## ğŸ“± Mobile-First Priorities

### Touch Targets
```css
/* Minimum sizes */
--touch-target-min: 44px;   /* iOS guideline */

/* Apply to all interactive elements */
.btn, .link, .card {
  min-height: 44px;
  min-width: 44px;
}
```

### Mobile Layout Adjustments
```
Desktop:    3-column (Feed + 2 Sidebars)
Tablet:     2-column (Feed + 1 Sidebar)
Mobile:     1-column (Feed only, sidebars collapse)

Bottom Navigation: Sticky on mobile
Floating Actions: Bottom-right on mobile
```

